snippet.title: Husky Express Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the first trailer for Husky Express revealed at Gstar 2008, a new MMORPG developed by DevCat and operated by Nexon. The game seems to revolve around players traveling on sleds with their dogs, adventuring through a snowy landscape. Husky Express definitely seems to bring something new to the online game genre!

Love MapleStory? Love playing Nexon games? Love MMORPGs? Love just playing games in general? Then check out Nautilus Port and join the community at: www.nautilusport.net
